'''加爾松潟湖大橋'''（{{lang-es|Puente de Laguna Garzón}}）是位於[[乌拉圭|乌拉圭]][[加爾松_(烏拉圭)|加爾松]]{{link-es|加爾松潟湖|Laguna Garzón}}的環狀[[橋|橋樑]]。大橋屬{{link-es|國道10號 (烏拉圭)|Ruta 10 (Uruguay)|國道10號}}的一部分，連接[[马尔多纳多省|马尔多纳多省]]及[[罗恰省|罗恰省]]兩省，由{{link-es|拉斐爾·維諾利|Rafael Viñoly}}設計，由薩塞姆（{{lang|es|Saceem}}）興建<ref name=Con/><ref name=Mirror/>。大橋於2015年12月22日通車，每天可通行多達約1000輛車輛架次<ref>{{Cite web|first=Jessica|last=Mairs|url=https://www.dezeen.com/2016/01/19/laguna-garzon-bridge-circular-rafael-vinoly-uruguay-lagoon/|title=Circular bridge by Rafael Viñoly spans Uruguay lagoon|date=2016-01-19|website=Dezeen|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805113053/https://www.dezeen.com/2016/01/19/laguna-garzon-bridge-circular-rafael-vinoly-uruguay-lagoon/|archive-date=2020-08-05|dead-url=no|accessdate=2020-10-20}}</ref>。

==設計==
大橋由拉斐爾·維諾利設計，由薩塞姆（{{lang|es|Saceem}}）興建，跨越位於烏拉圭加爾松的加爾松潟湖，並連接馬爾多納多省及羅恰省兩省，以取代位於該位置的筏通道<ref name=Con>{{Cite web|title=The long-awaited Laguna Garzon Bridge is set up - Consultatio Real Estate|url=http://www.consultatio.com.ar/en/2016/01/the-long-awaited-laguna-garzon-bridge-is-set-up/|website=Consultatio Real Estate|date=2016-01-06|access-date=2016-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106205539/http://www.consultatio.com.ar/en/2016/01/the-long-awaited-laguna-garzon-bridge-is-set-up/|archive-date=2020-01-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=Mirror>{{Cite web|title=Can you guess why architects built a road bridge circular instead of straight?|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/can-you-guess-architects-built-7254555|website=Mirror|date=2016-01-27|access-date=2016-01-28|first=Rhian|last=Lubin|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607080134/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/can-you-guess-architects-built-7254555|archive-date=2019-06-07}}</ref>。大橋的環狀設計可迫使駕駛者減速，並容許行人沿單向環狀路線通行（雖然在陸地上建造同樣的環狀道路可減省一半的費用，並起到相同的效果）。大橋的環狀設計主要出於美觀考量，並同時增強橋體強度、使駕駛者減速及安全性提高等效果<ref>{{cite web|author=Huffington Post|date=2016-01-27|publisher=National Sun Times|url=http://national.suntimes.com/world-news/7/72/2503378/this-circular-bridge-encourages-drivers-to-slow-down-and-take-in-the-view|title=This Circular Bridge Encourages Drivers To Slow Down And Take In The View|accessdate=2016-05-19|quote=...Each half circle on the bridge acts as a one-way street ... drivers will have to slow down to cross, ...|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623231807/http://national.suntimes.com/world-news/7/72/2503378/this-circular-bridge-encourages-drivers-to-slow-down-and-take-in-the-view|archivedate=2016-06-23}}</ref>。

